<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.1.1">
<l>vāṉa vartaṅkaḷ cintai pōlaveṉ neñca</l>
<l>mēyiṉi tuvan tumātava</l>
<l>māṉa vartaṅkaḷ cintai yamarntuṟai kiṉṟaventai</l>
<l>kāṉa variṭu kāra kiṟpukai yōṅku vēṅkaṭam</l>
<l>mēvi māṇkuṟa</l>
<l>ḷāṉa vantaṇaṟ kiṉṟa ṭimaittoḻil pūṇṭāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My heart, sweetly rejoicing like the minds of the celestials,</l>
<l rend="indent">today you assumed the duty of service</l>
<l>To our father who abides resting in the minds of men of great merit,</l>
<l>The brahmin who was a novice dwarf, dwelling on Vēṅkaṭam</l>
<l>Where smoke rises from dark eaglewood that woodsmen offer.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
